Subject: Re: [T2] Oil cooler leaks?

I would look real close at the oil pressure sending unit... it is above the
cooler, leaks under pressure when the engine is running, and fools you into
thinking the cooler is leaking......


> How can I tell if an oil leak is coming from the oil cooler, or something
